high_descs: Turn around, go forward, turn left, move to the sink.
Pick up the bottle on the back of the sink.
Bring the bottle to the left to the fridge.
Chill the bottle in the fridge.
Take the chilled bottle from the fridge, turn around, move to the stove, face the stove.
Open the cabinet right of the stove, put bottle in that cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bottle in the cabinet right of the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and head towards the sink on your left.
Take the wine bottle on the sink counter.
Turn left and walk towards the fridge to your right.
Place the bottle in the fridge, let it cool, and then take it back out.
Turn around and walk towards the oven on your right.
Open the cabinet to the right of the oven and place the bottle inside.
anns.task_desc: Place the cooled wine bottle inside the cabinet to the right of the oven.
